      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIGERMAC (1) put the writing on the wall when he came from a much wider barrier and finished third last start at this venue. Reaching peak fitness now and should get his chance from the inside draw. MY ROCK MOVES (3) did a very good job to come from a back row draw and score by more than 9 metres in a nice return to form at this circuit and distance last start. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Primary contender. This is the lowest-graded race ALLSOPP (6) has tackled for a while and he strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance so could produce his best in this line up. MAJOR MICKEY (9) is suited returning to Tamworth having won the last time he raced here three back.",
